PuppySmash - AI-Powered Dog Identity Cards

  Transform your dog's photo into a shareable identity card that celebrates their unique story.

  PuppySmash is an iOS app that uses advanced AI to analyze dog photos and generate beautiful, shareable identity cards showing breed mix, age estimation,
  rarity scores, and uniqueness statistics. Built with SwiftUI and powered by cutting-edge machine learning APIs, it delivers a delightful experience for dog
  owners to discover and share what makes their pet special.

  Key Features

