  - Precise breed detection using NANOBANANA API for superior accuracy
  - Multi-factor age estimation combining facial features, body proportions, and breed context
  - Smart uniqueness scoring with celebratory language (no negative messaging about mixed breeds)
  - Local Vision framework integration for instant dog detection

  ðŸ“± Native iOS Experience
  - SwiftUI-first architecture with 60 FPS performance
  - Seamless camera and photo library integration
  - Works completely offline for core features
  - Firebase integration for cloud sync and account management

  ðŸŽ¨ Beautiful Share Cards
  - Customizable identity cards in 9:16 (Stories) and 1:1 (Feed) formats
  - Multiple themes including Playful and Minimal designs
  - Toggle data elements on/off for personalization
  - High-quality export to Photos with proper permissions

  âš¡ Performance Optimized
  - Sub-5 second photo analysis including API calls
  - <100MB memory usage during processing
