  Technical Highlights

  Architecture
  - Clean SwiftUI app structure with MVVM patterns
  - Reactive state management using @Published and Combine
  - Modular service layer for analysis, storage, and networking
  - Comprehensive error handling with user-friendly messaging

  AI Integration
  - Vision framework for local dog detection and cropping
  - NANOBANANA API for cloud-based breed classification
  - Custom algorithms for age estimation and uniqueness scoring
  - CoreML optimization for on-device processing

  Data & Privacy
  - Core Data persistence with smart cleanup policies
  - Firebase Firestore for cloud sync (optional)
  - Complete privacy controls and transparent data handling
  - "For entertainment purposes" disclaimers throughout

  Quality Assurance
  - Comprehensive accessibility support with VoiceOver
  - Dynamic Type support for all text sizes
  - Full Dark/Light mode compatibility
  - Automated visual testing with iOS Simulator validation

  Development Approach

  Built using a visual-first development methodology with real iOS Simulator screenshot validation. The app leverages automated accessibility compliance
  checking and multi-device consistency testing to ensure a polished user experience across all supported devices.

  The codebase follows strict performance targets and celebrates dogs of all breeds with positive, encouraging language throughout the interface.
